      "title": "The Psychology of Attention",
      "abstract": "Part 1 Attention and perception: selective attention divided attention attentional set capacity and selection - theorizing about attention. Part 2 Attention, memory and action: central processing limitations in sensorimotor tasks attention and memory automaticity, effort and control."
